      "id": "PopularPost232289",
      "post_content": "\\*Coughs\\* Okay, in pure mono red burn, this is ridiculous, another playset of lightning bolt, essentially. Here's how it works:  \n1) Load your deck with 40% lands, and inexpensive red instants and sorceries that deal cheap, effective damage, including four copies of [Lightning Bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt), [Chain Lightning](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chain Lightning), [Lava Spike](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lava Spike), [Shard Volley](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shard Volley), [Browbeat](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Browbeat), and other such cards.  \n2) Include four copies of this and four copies of [Fiery Temper](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fiery Temper)  \n3) Cast this when you have one other card in your hand and it is Fiery Temper. (should be easy when you're emptying your hand of 1 spell on T1, then 2 spells on T2, then 3 on T3, etc...)  \n4) Have fun with all the lightning (read: consistent T4 wins) and stop rating this card so low.",
      "posted_by": "gman92",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost232289\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">*Coughs* Okay, in pure mono red burn, this is ridiculous, another playset of lightning bolt, essentially. Here's how it works:<br/>1) Load your deck with 40% lands, and inexpensive red instants and sorceries that deal cheap, effective damage, including four copies of <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lightning Bolt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt\">Lightning Bolt</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Chain Lightning\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Chain Lightning\">Chain Lightning</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lava Spike\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lava Spike\">Lava Spike</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Shard Volley\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shard Volley\">Shard Volley</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Browbeat\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Browbeat\">Browbeat</a>, and other such cards.<br/>2) Include four copies of this and four copies of <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fiery Temper\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fiery Temper\">Fiery Temper</a><br/>3) Cast this when you have one other card in your hand and it is Fiery Temper. (should be easy when you're emptying your hand of 1 spell on T1, then 2 spells on T2, then 3 on T3, etc...)<br/>4) Have fun with all the lightning (read: consistent T4 wins) and stop rating this card so low.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleRe