      "post_content": "You guys must be underestimating the power of 3 damage for ![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol). Discarding at random is easy to control (i.e. discard [Fiery Temper](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fiery Temper)) in Mono-Red, since you will be playing your hand out very, very quickly.  \n...  \nBut yeah, there's better burn out there. The real question is whether this is better than [Shard Volley](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shard Volley).",
